text: PKN can mean: *Pertti Kurikan Nimipäivät, a Finnish punk band *A member of the protein kinase family of enzymes **PKN1, protein kinase N1 *Protestant Church in the Netherlands *Personal knowledge networking *Program Khidmat Negara, Malaysia's National Service program *The Palace of Culture and Science, the tallest building in Poland *A variant version of the PK machine gun *PKN, the IATA code of Iskandar Airport in Indonesia * Polish Committee for Standardization, Polski Komitet Normalizacyjny
title: PKN
